&lt;p&gt;&lt;strong&gt;Business Development Associate-Referral Partner&lt;/strong&gt;&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;p&gt;&lt;strong&gt;NO RESUME NEEDED!&amp;nbsp;&lt;/strong&gt;&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;p&gt;&lt;strong&gt;3MG Solutions&lt;/strong&gt;&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;p&gt;3MG Solutions, LLC is one of the fastest-growing residential and commercial roofing contractors in the United States. With offices across Florida, Missouri, Georgia and Kansas, we pride ourselves on our team-centric culture, mutual respect, and active community involvement.&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;p&gt;&lt;strong&gt;Why Join 3MG Solutions?&lt;/strong&gt;&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;ul&gt;
&lt;li&gt;We’re one of the nation’s top roofing contractors - and still growing (residential, commercial, repairs, trades, and specialty roofing).&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;We are Owens Corning Platinum Preferred Contractor giving our homeowners unmatched warranty protection and exclusive access to premium products&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;Proud Partner of the St. Louis Cardinals&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;Proud Partner of UCF Athletics&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;/ul&gt;
&lt;p&gt;&lt;strong&gt;Position Summary&lt;/strong&gt;&amp;nbsp;&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;p data-start=&quot;156&quot; data-end=&quot;435&quot;&gt;We are seeking motivated and well-connected Referral Partners to help generate qualified leads for our sales team. This is a commission-based opportunity ideal for professionals with strong networks who want to earn by connecting homeowners and property owners with our services.&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;p data-start=&quot;437&quot; data-end=&quot;636&quot;&gt;Referral Partners play a key role in expanding our reach by identifying potential customers and introducing them to our team. You’ll earn commissions on closed business resulting from your referrals.&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;h4 data-start=&quot;0&quot; data-end=&quot;83&quot;&gt;Key Responsibilities&lt;/h4&gt;
&lt;ul&gt;
&lt;li data-start=&quot;673&quot; data-end=&quot;727&quot;&gt;Identify and refer qualified leads to our sales team&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li data-start=&quot;730&quot; data-end=&quot;845&quot;&gt;Build and maintain relationships within your network (homeowners, property managers, realtors, contractors, etc.)&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li data-start=&quot;848&quot; data-end=&quot;914&quot;&gt;Share basic information about our services and value proposition&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li data-start=&quot;917&quot; data-end=&quot;966&quot;&gt;Submit referrals through our designated process&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li data-start=&quot;969&quot; data-end=&quot;1045&quot;&gt;Maintain professionalism and brand integrity when representing our company&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;/ul&gt;
&lt;h3 data-start=&quot;1107&quot; data-end=&quot;1128&quot;&gt;Ideal Candidate&lt;/h3&gt;
&lt;ul&gt;
&lt;li data-start=&quot;1132&quot; data-end=&quot;1181&quot;&gt;Well-connected within the community or industry&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li data-start=&quot;1184&quot; data-end=&quot;1239&quot;&gt;Strong communication and relationship-building skills&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li data-start=&quot;1242&quot; data-end=&quot;1277&quot;&gt;Self-motivated and results-driven&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li data-start=&quot;1280&quot; data-end=&quot;1310&quot;&gt;Professional and trustworthy&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li data-start=&quot;1313&quot; data-end=&quot;1438&quot;&gt;Experience in real estate, property management, construction, insurance, or related industries is a plus (but not required)&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;/ul&gt;
&lt;p&gt;&amp;nbsp;&lt;/p&gt;

